    "name": "野靛花农场",
    "steam_appid": 1751350,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751350/extras/4dd4e57be341b4c409255ee2269b2eff.poster.avif?t=1739869091\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751350/extras/4dd4e57be341b4c409255ee2269b2eff.webm?t=1739869091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>你好哇，小牛仔！你从你叔叔那里继承了野靛花农场，要在西部开展新的生活！但偏远地区的生活可不会像你在故事里听到那般诗情画意。沙砾公司图谋不轨，要把草原变成一台盈利机器。与周边的汤博维尔的镇民合作，帮助野靛花农场重拾往日辉煌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751350/extras/1bf3ad527411e6a8ae1cfe3c18e04653.poster.avif?t=1739869091\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751350/extras/1bf3ad527411e6a8ae1cfe3c18e04653.webm?t=1739869091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>只要你努力做一个善于经营的牛仔，就会发现草原上的资源并不稀缺。采集稻草，做一根绳子——然后就可以套来属于你的第一匹野马了。不过，假如你想循序渐进，可以先拿驴子罗茜练练手。真正的牛仔需要配一把六发左轮手枪，以便在必要时匡扶正义、在荒野中保护自己。不过你要知道怎么制作才行。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751350/extras/65a9cc819369624a9fea88c4910317f8.poster.avif?t=1739869091\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751350/extras/65a9cc819369624a9fea88c4910317f8.webm?t=1739869091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>结束一整天的漫长冒险后，你这样的牛仔最需要的就是找个地方好好休息。挽起袖子，拿起工具，开始建造你梦想中的农场。种植作物，耕种土地，为你的农场配备马厩、鸡舍和工坊。最后，可以根据自己的喜好布置你的新家——有壁炉的地方就是家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751350/extras/91f4bd4016dd56c72afd4258d3c16690.poster.avif?t=1739869091\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751350/extras/91f4bd4016dd56c72afd4258d3c16690.webm?t=1739869091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>你可以单人游玩，也可以与至多三名玩家组队。共同努力工作，收集可利用的资源，打造西部最好的牧场，迎着落日开启精彩牛仔人生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
